          </div>

          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-accent/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-accent" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path d="M2 6a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v8a2 2 0 01-2 2H4a2 2 0 01-2-2V6zM14.553 7.106A1 1 0 0014 8v4a1 1 0 00.553.894l2 1A1 1 0 0018 13V7a1 1 0 00-1.447-.894l-2 1z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Telehealth Platforms</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Custom telehealth solutions with video visits, remote monitoring, and virtual care coordination.</p>
            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-500 space-y-2">
              <li>‚Ä¢ HIPAA-compliant video</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Mobile apps for patients</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ RPM device integration</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-secondary/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-secondary" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path d="M13 6a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zM18 8a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM14 15a4 4 0 00-8 0v3h8v-3z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">AI & Clinical Intelligence</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">AI-powered clinical decision support, diagnostic assistance, and predictive analytics.</p>
            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-500 space-y-2">
              <li>‚Ä¢ Clinical documentation AI</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Diagnostic image analysis</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Readmission prediction</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-green-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-green-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 4a2 2 0 00-2 2v4a2 2 0 002 2V6h10a2 2 0 00-2-2H4zm2 6a2 2 0 012-2h8a2 2 0 012 2v4a2 2 0 01-2 2H8a2 2 0 01-2-2v-4zm6 4a2 2 0 100-4 2 2 0 000 4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Revenue Cycle & Claims</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Automated claims processing, denial management, and revenue cycle optimization.</p>
            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-500 space-y-2">
              <li>‚Ä¢ Claims automation</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Denial prediction</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Prior authorization</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8">
