              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Interoperability & HIE</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Health information exchange solutions enabling secure data sharing across organizations.</p>
            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-500 space-y-2">
              <li>‚Ä¢ FHIR API development</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ HIE connectivity</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Data normalization</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-red-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-red-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M2.166 4.999A11.954 11.954 0 0010 1.944 11.954 11.954 0 0017.834 5c.11.65.166 1.32.166 2.001 0 5.225-3.34 9.67-8 11.317C5.34 16.67 2 12.225 2 7c0-.682.057-1.35.166-2.001zm11.541 3.708a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Compliance & Security</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">HIPAA compliance assessments, security implementations, and ongoing monitoring.</p>
            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-500 space-y-2">
              <li>‚Ä¢ HIPAA gap analysis</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Security architecture</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Audit preparation</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Compliance Section -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-montserrat font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-6">
              HIPAA Compliance Built In
            </h2>
